groups.label: This refers to your usual way of life in recent times.
Even if you haven‘t done some of these things recently try' to work out how they would have affected you.
Use the following scale to choose the most appropriate number for each situation:
It is important that you answer ouch question as best you can.
Sitting, inactive in a public place (e.g. a theatre or a meeting)
As a passenger in a car for an hour without a break
Lying down to rest in the afternoon when circumstances permit
Sitting quietly after a lunch without alcohol
In a car, while stopped for a few minutes in the trafﬁc
